data.description: Unique Single Detached Home in the Heart of the Historic District of Bordentown. Year Built 2012.  High Ceilings on all Levels, including the  Basement. Fully renovated and updated, this property offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms - with one bedroom and full bath on the main level. Two bedrooms and a full bathroom on 2nd Floor.  Poured Concrete Basement with Laundry area. Additional features include: Freshly painted in a neutral tone throughout. Luxury Vinyl Flooring throughout. Central Air Conditioning. Driveway offering off street parking. Private backyard. Full Enclosed front porch. Roof (2012). Hot Water Heater (2023). HVAC (2012). New Washing Machine (2023) Located down the road from Farnsworth Ave /Downtown Bordentown. Close to local Schools. Enjoy all that Bordentown has to offer with its many restaurants, shops, and local festivities. Bundle with  purchase  of  Lot at 51 West Street.
